{"id":6250,"date":"2021-02-24T10:27:18","date_gmt":"2021-02-24T03:27:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=6250"},"modified":"2023-08-03T11:19:33","modified_gmt":"2023-08-03T04:19:33","slug":"rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni","title":{"rendered":"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Modero &#8211; M\u00e3 Giovanni"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080; font-size: 85%;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Modero &#8211; M\u00e3 Giovanni<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eb9p hay r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1edfi hai l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i k\u00e9o so le nhau, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i. V\u1edbi m\u1eabu m\u00e3 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc phong ph\u00fa r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7425 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-2-510x680.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080; font-size: 85%;\"><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">C\u00f4ng n\u0103ng \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t, d\u1ec5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng. Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1ng ph\u1ee7, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i mang phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0u sang tr\u1ecdng b\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p, thao t\u00e1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, d\u1ec5 v\u1ec7 sinh, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7424 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-1.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-1-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-1-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-mod