20\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-2-743x400.jpg 743w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-2-1400x754.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-2-768x413.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-2-1536x827.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-2-510x275.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2006px) 100vw, 2006px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6741 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1858\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1.jpg 1858w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1-688x400.jpg 688w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1-1376x800.jpg 1376w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1-768x446.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1-1536x893.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/thong-so-phu-kien-rem-cau-vong-1-1-510x296.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1858px) 100vw, 1858px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 Ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c bao g\u1ed3m: H\u1ed9p ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9o, Thanh \u0111\u00e1y v\u00e0 v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 H\u1ed9p ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n r\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng h\u1ed9p kim nh\u00f4m s\u01a1n t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 n\u0103m. H\u1ed9p ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0u v\u1edbi m\u00e0u v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">-H\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9o b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ef1a cao c\u1ea5p si\u00eau b\u1ec1n. D\u00e2y k\u00e9o r\u00e8m b\u1eb1ng d\u00e2y cao c\u1ea5p<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">-Thanh \u0111\u00e1y m\u00e0n c\u1eeda H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p kim nh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u00f4m. Thanh \u0111\u00e1y c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi h\u1ed9p r\u00e8m<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">-V\u1ea3i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">+ L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i d\u1ec7t t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100%<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">+ L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i l\u01b0\u1edbi r\u00e8m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1edbi cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i cao, ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee9t h\u00e3y<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">+ \u0110\u1ed9 d\u00e0y v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 l\u01b0\u1edbi theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp qua khe l\u01b0\u1edbi<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080; font-size: 85%;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng M\u00e3 Giovanni (GN 501 \u2013 GN 505)<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7426 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"827\" height=\"824\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3.jpg 827w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-401x400.jpg 401w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-803x800.jpg 803w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-768x765.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-510x508.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/rem-cau-vong-modero-ma-giovanni-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 827px) 100vw, 827px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng m\u00e3 <span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>GIOVANNI<\/strong><\/span> l\u00e0 <strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">884.000\u0110<\/span>\u00a0<\/strong>. R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 5-20% t\u00f9y v\u00e0o kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00e3 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. Li\u00ean h\u1ec7\u00a0<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a style=\"color: #ff0000;\" href=\"tel:0964546888\"><strong>0964546888<\/strong><\/a><\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng M\u00e3<strong> <span style=\"color: #000080;\">GIOVANNI<\/span>:<\/strong>\u00a0100% Polyeste<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 Kh\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m l\u00e0: 280cm\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 \u0110\u1ed9 d\u00e0y c\u1ee7a v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m l\u00e0: 0.55mm<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 Tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m: 145g\/m2<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 \u0110\u1ed9 l\u1eb7p: v\u1ea3i 75mm\/sheer 50 mm<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">\u2013 Xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080; font-size: 85%;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi mua R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n nay tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u00e3ng r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 v\u1ea3i r\u00e8m t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c n\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng cao m\u00e0 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i s\u1ea5p s\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. V\u00ec v\u00e2y, R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng Modero th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 1 v\u1ec1 R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh tr\u00ean Website c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7122\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1276\" height=\"650\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-2.jpg 1276w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-2-785x400.jpg 785w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-2-768x391.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-2-510x260.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1276px) 100vw, 1276px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u website kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u01b0 nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c R\u00e8m c\u1eeda, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng chu\u1ea9n v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh n\u00ean kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb mua ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng. Do v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u01b0 \u00fd<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7123\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-vol-9-phu-thanh-1-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb b\u00e1n r\u00e8m UY T\u00cdN, TRUNG TH\u1ef0C l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch T\u1ed0T NH\u1ea4T b\u1ea1n mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m CH\u1ea4T L\u01af\u1ee2NG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n H\u1ee2P L\u00dd<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 85%;\"><strong>R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u2013 T\u1ed5ng \u0110\u1ea1i L\u00fd U\u1ef7 Quy\u1ec1n Ph\u00e2n Ph\u1ed1i R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng Modero H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Modero l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c ng\u00e0nh R\u00e8m C\u1eeda ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n m\u1eabu m\u00e3, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd CO,CQ\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n d\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 thi c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh r\u00e8m c\u1eeda l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0, nh\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1eaft, Nh\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, qu\u00e1n cafe,\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7121\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1148\" height=\"749\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh.jpg 1148w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-613x400.jpg 613w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-768x501.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-modero-vol-9-phu-thanh-510x333.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1148px) 100vw, 1148px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 85%; color: #000080;\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Modero \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">V\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cho c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modero<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7420 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/rem-cau-vong-dep-ma-nicole-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/rem-cau-vong-dep-ma-nicole-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/rem-cau-vong-dep-ma-nicole-1-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/rem-cau-vong-dep-ma-nicole-1-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/