-801x800.jpg 801w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-tai-cau-giay-3-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-tai-cau-giay-3-768x767.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-tai-cau-giay-3-1536x1534.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-tai-cau-giay-3-510x509.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-tai-cau-giay-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7277\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-4-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng Modero ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0o?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">V\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cho c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modero\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i b\u1ecb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o gay g\u1eaft. Cho n\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Do v\u1eady r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111an xen gi\u1eefa ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp voan, khi k\u00e9o r\u00e8m so le r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eafn n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, l\u1edbp voan s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00ed b\u00e1ch.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Modero c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi thao t\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec3u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng theo \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8606 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-500x400.jpg 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-1000x800.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-khach-510x408.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang t\u01b0, c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u0129nh, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 \u0111i v\u00e0o gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o b\u1edfi r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng y\u00eau t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Modero v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eeda s\u1ed5, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. M\u1eabu r\u00e8m sang tr\u1ecdng, nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8607 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu-500x400.jpg 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu-1000x800.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/cac-mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-ngu-510x408.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 ph\u00f2ng B\u1ebfp<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 ph\u00f2ng B\u1ebfp l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a hai lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nhau, gi\u00fap b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m tr\u1edf n\u00ean l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn. Hai l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0i h\u00f2a khi mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8608 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep-500x400.jpg 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep-1000x800.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-bep-510x408.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng cho Ph\u00f2ng T\u1eafm<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Sau nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, s\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea3 m\u00ecnh trong l\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m \u00e1p nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. V\u00e0 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 che ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian th\u1eadt l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n v\u00e0 k\u00edn \u0111\u00e1o trong c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5m n\u01b0\u1edbc, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n t\u00e1ch khu v\u1ef1c \u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c kh\u00f4 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch trang tr\u00ed l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft cho nh\u1eefng c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8609 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam-500x400.jpg 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam-1000x800.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-phong-tam-510x408.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng cho v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u1eefa b\u1edfi v\u00ec m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng che ch\u1eafn cao, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng gian v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean trang nh\u00e3 v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8610 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong.png 2000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong-500x400.png 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong-1000x800.png 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong-768x614.png 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/mau-rem-cau-vong-cho-van-phong-1536x1229.